title: Hear Travis Scott’s New Single, ‘Highest in the Room’
text:
Doleful guitar plucking underscores Travis Scott’s new single, “Highest in the Room.” The song is all about how successful and stoned Scott is, but the guitar says it’s not enough to keep him happy. On Tuesday, TMZ broke the news that Scott and Kylie Jenner were taking a break. Later in the week, Kylie was spotted outside her former paramour Tyga’s studio, and rumors erupted (and were squashed) that the two were back together. Suffice to say, Travis Scott’s personal life has been in the news a lot this week. And it’s not a 2019 break-up without a single.

Related
description: Travis Scott released a new song, “Highest in the Room,” the same week it was announced that he and Kylie Jenner were taking a break. Sources say the two don’t consider it a permanent rupture. The song brags about how successful and stoned Scott is.
